\c 49
\s Zvose panyika zvinopfuura
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; Pisarema ravanakomana vaKora.
\p
\v 1 Inzwai chinhu ichi, imi vanhu vose;
\s Teererai, imi mose mugere panyika;
\p
\v 2 Imi vaduku navanokudzwa, Vapfumi navarombo pamwechete.
\p
\v 3 Muromo wangu uchataura huchenjeri;
\s Uye kufunga kwomwoyo wangu kuchava nenjere.
\p
\v 4 Ndicharerekera nzeve yangu inzwe mufananidzo;
\s Ndichadudza shoko rangu
\s rakavanzika nembira.
\p
\v 5 Ndichatya neiko pamisi yezvakaipa, Kana zvakaipa, zvavanoda kundidzinga, zvichindikomba?
\p
\v 6 Ivo, vanovimba nepfuma yavo, Vanozvikudza pamusoro
\s pokuwanda kwepfuma yavo;
\p
\v 7 Hapana angatongodzikinura hama yake,
\s Kana kupa Mwari rudzikinuro pamusoro pake;
\p
\v 8 (Nokuti rudzikinuro rwemweya yawo runokosha,
\s Runofanira kuregwa nokusingaperi;)
\p
\v 9 Kuti arambe ari mupenyu misi yose, Arege kuona kuora.
\p
\v 1 Â° Nokuti anoona kuti vachenjeri vanofa,
\s Benzi neasina njere vanopera pamwechete,
\s Vachisiyira vamwe pfuma yavo.
\p
\v 11 Vanofunga pamwoyo pavo kuti dzimba dzavo dzichagara nokusingaperi,
\s Nougaro hwavo kusvikira
\s kumarudzi avo ose;
\s Nyika dzavo vanodzitumidza mazita avo.
\p
\v 12 Asi munhu haagari achikudzwa, Akafanana nemhuka dzinopera.
\p
\v 13 Iyi ndiyo nzira yamapenzi; Kunyange zvakadaro vanhu vanovatevera
\s vachitenda zvavanotaura.
\p
\v 14 Vakatarirwa Sheori samakwai;
\s Rufu ruchava mufudzi wavo;
\s Vakarurama vachabata hushe
\s pamusoro
\s pavo mangwanani;
\s Kunaka kwavo kuchangoparadzwa neSheori, kuti kurege kuva nougaro.
\p
\v 15 Asi Mwari achadzikinura mweya wangu pasimba reSheori;
\s Nokuti iye achandigamuchira.
\p
\v 16 Usatya hako iwe kana mumwe munhu achifumiswa,
\s Kana pfuma yeimba yake ichiwedzerwa;
\p
\v 17 Nokuti kana achifa hapana
\s chaachaenda nacho;
\s Mukurumbira wake haungaburuki uchimutevera.
\p
\v 18 Kunyange paupenyu hwake waikorokotedza mweya wake, (Kunyange vanhu vaikurumbidza kana uchizviitira zvakanaka),
\p
\v 19 Achaenda iye kurudzi
\s rwarnadzibaba ake;
\s Ivo havangatongooni chiedza nokusingaperi.
\p
\v 20 Munhu, anokudzwa, asina njere, Akafanana nemhuka dzinopera.
